Package com.saicone.rtag

Class RtagEditor<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.saicone.rtag.RtagEditor<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Parent object type.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RtagBlock, RtagEntity, RtagItem
    public abstract class RtagEditor<T>
extends Object
    RtagEditor abstract class who edit any object with NBTTagCompound inside.
    Also provide methods to easy-edit object tags using a Rtag instance.
